## AUTODOC-IT 1.13 - THE PROGRAMMERS GUIDE
##
## This is a first approach to get ALL those autodocs linked together with
## amigaguide, the new document-help-format by Commodore.
## With amigaguide, you should have received some utilities, which
## are useful for converting autodoc-compatible (!) textfiles into the
## amigaguide/hypertext format.
## Do not use this database without having converted those files or
## autodoc-it will not work.
## Please read the short manual: Getting_Started.doc before using
## autodoc-it.
## Not included in this archive are, of course, the amigaguide package and
## the autodoc-files, because they are © by Commodore and available only to
## registered developers!
##
## You may redistribute this database and use it anyway you like, as long as this
## header and all files (see archive.txt) stay in it. Take a look at the docs
## for the copyright notice.
##
## Following are the non-system doc files supported (you have to convert
## the appropriate doc files included in the several packages of the
## programs:
##
## - reqtools
## - iff.library
## - appshell (DEVCON)
##
## Version History: V1.0  - January    1992
##                  V1.01 - February   1992
##                  V1.1  - April      1992 
##                  V1.11 - April      1992
##                  V1.12 - May        1992
##                  V1.13 - June       1992
## $VER V1.13 June 1992 by Voyager@Treff.zer

